  <description><![CDATA[<p>Set in a panoramic position on the Golfo Delle Saline, the local town of Palau is only 3kms away.</p>
<p>The hotels pools have views across the beach and is surrounded wooden sunbathing platforms, the rooms are set a little back in the mature Mediterranean gardens enjoying cooling sea breezes and view across the Maddalena archipelago and Bear Rock.</p>
<p>Cala di Lepre is ideal for families wanting to spend time together relaxing or taking part in activities and you won’t have to compromise on comfort. Parents can enjoy their time while the children take advantage of the complimentary Mini &amp; Junior Clubs for children aged 3 to 14.</p>
<p>The “de’ Ea Marina Spa offers a relaxing sanctuary and the lounge bar an ideal location for evening cocktails. The two onsite restaurants serve traditional flavours and cuisine using locally sources Sardinian produce as well as international dishes.</p>]]></description>
