  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>Rooms are located in either the Il Parco areas which is a little further from the central building and offers a little more seclusion while the Il Golfo rooms are closer to the main facilities.</p>
<p>Standard rooms – Double or twin beds up to 26m2 in size, ideal for 2 adults and the extra bed for children up to 13. All have verandas or terraces and rooms with sea view available at a supplement.</p>
<p>Deluxe rooms sleeping up to 3 adults and 1 infant and suites sleeping up to 4 adults are available at a supplement.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
